name: Start With Nothing On
description:
Start With Nothing On

Streak your way to victory and put some clothes on!

How To Play

Arrow keys/ WASD to move Ctrl/ Right click to jump

Bit of a shorter jam this time, only had a day and a half to put it together. Would have been nice to get some more gameplay in but we hope you enjoy!
